Àtụ:Infobox badminton player
Clement Ebiowo Krobakpo (amuru 1 Julaị 1994) bu onye egwu badminton nke Naijiria
O nwetara ihe nrite ọla nchara abụọ n'egwuregwu Afrịka nke afọ 2015 n'asọmpi ndi nwoke n'ọkwa otu na ndi otu egwuregwu
Krobakpo gbakwara asọmpi n'egwuregwu Afrịka nke afọ 2019, wee nweta ọla edo ndị otu agwakọtara
